          <p>Lab-grown diamonds are real diamonds. I want to get that on the table before anything else because most of the confusion in this space starts with that question. I'm Suman Smith, and I've been sourcing lab-grown diamonds for Lux Jewels since 2007. In 2015, I became the first jeweller in Canada to commit exclusively to lab-grown stones - over ten years before "ethical diamond" became a marketing line for chains that still primarily sell mined. I've watched this market build from a niche to a mainstream choice, and I've seen what buyers get wrong when they're researching it. This guide covers all of it.</p>

